</ul>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=2002_Gujarat_violence&action=edit&section=22.php.html" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="References">References</span></h2>
<div class="reflist references-column-width" style="-moz-column-width: 30em; -webkit-column-width: 30em; column-width: 30em; list-style-type: decimal;">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-790_254_humans-1"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-790_254_humans_1-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-790_254_humans_1-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-790_254_humans_1-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation news"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/articleshow/1106699.cms">"790 Muslims, 254 Hindus perished in post-Godhra"</a>. <i>Times of India</i> (India). 11 May 2005<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/articleshow/1106699.cms">http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/articleshow/1106699.cms</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 4 February 2011</span>.</span></span></li>
